{"tid":1853103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"認住呢個唔知醜又黑心嘅尖沙咀診所助護 (咒人肺炎)","createTime":"2020-01-30T19:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T10:33:44.000Z","uid":347270,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4f05eb98cf47de5cfcabf127792424d1b3a65a80","tid":1853103,"uid":347270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T19:02:57.000Z","msg":"我朋友稱為A<br />\n條唔知醜又黑心嘅bitch稱為B<br />\nA前幾年就同B拍拖，大約一年半，當時B叫A幫佢開電話號碼(佢話會自己交)。A幫佢開左兩個號碼後兩個月，佢有日突然block曬A所有可以聯絡佢嘅渠道，後尾先知B同左第二個一齊，啲電話費B當然冇再交啦。佢嗰兩個plan加埋都要五百幾，當時A冇咁多多餘錢去交，又搵唔到B，就比電話公司瘋狂打電話追比違約費，最後仲比收錢公司係咁打黎追佢。比人煩左幾個月A就諗住交返錢開返嗰兩個號碼黎用，然後嗰兩個號碼有大耳窿一直打電話黎叫還錢。原來B叫A開嗰兩個電話係用黎借大耳窿錢，最後A就怕會有啲咩，所以就比曬啲違約費唔要嗰兩個號碼就算<br />\n<br />\n隔左一年當A有新女友，B知道左之後係咁不停打電話(<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">凌晨幾點打十幾個電話黎 </span></strong>)同用不同渠道搵返A(當時B係有男友仲同居)，仲要係咁騷擾A嘅女友(<strong>最變態嘅係[red]佢hack入A嘅fb ig搵到佢女友電話 然後wts A女友話會搶返A返去[red] </strong>)當初又係佢飛人，人地有女友又要搞9人，真係百思不得其解。<br />\n<br />\nA就見難得搵到佢就叫佢還錢，搞左一輪B話會還$4000，但A唔止比左呢個數，覺得收返$4000都已經好好。佢地傾好左一個月還1000，但每次叫B還佢都話自己冇錢，又唔係唔還，但講左幾次都係冇還過，之後每次都係A話「一係我上你公司搵你還，一係我拎我地嘅對話入小額錢債到告你」佢先會還錢。<br />\n<br />\n到琴日B又諗住拖住先(但其實B每個月月尾出糧)A就話搵佢新男還，之後都傾好左下個月尾先再還錢，但佢突然還曬所有錢，仲要咒9A，之後block埋A。其實A都唔知佢男友係邊個大9佢姐。A心諗「當年你比左幾次綠帽我戴最後仲要飛左我，我仲幫你頂左萬幾蚊電話費，我都未咒你有愛滋死，我追返我應有嘅野仲要比你咒」然後我都覺得呢個女人好痴線，所以幫我朋友叫大家要小心呢個女人 <br />\n叫<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Scarlett 古嘉慧 住元朗 佢成日喺交友app識人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AL8jiiH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAL8jiiH.png&h=54b6cd4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pUv5YmS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpUv5YmS.jpg&h=0aba7fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oV0hPtH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoV0hPtH.jpg&h=3685eb1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WLoSDm9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWLoSDm9.jpg&h=2b2a3cf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uAL5Yni.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuAL5Yni.jpg&h=293970d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aeLBkAH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaeLBkAH.jpg&h=f66bd80e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sA2ssfM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsA2ssfM.jpg&h=bce6e788&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcff5ec1caa843bcc17f9e0cd5bc638cfc96b60b","tid":1853103,"uid":13378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T19:11:20.000Z","msg":"好小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38034d17587e7e67e136f0bf2cdbf7cf6b5e20c","tid":1853103,"uid":318051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T19:16:22.000Z","msg":"人無恥就無敵<br />\n睇開啲啦"},{"pid":"ce94686a1c9736ed4fde4e39c6dd87997859a3e5","tid":1853103,"uid":347270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcff5ec1caa843bcc17f9e0cd5bc638cfc96b60b","tid":1853103,"uid":13378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T19:11:20.000Z","msg":"好小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T19:16:35.000Z","msg":"當你比佢幾晚都凌晨幾點打十幾廿個電話黎，仲要搵埋你女友同屋企人，煩足你幾個月，你就唔會覺小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d78b25a902bb4106294cde7fca3b894ae537430","tid":1853103,"uid":347270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b38034d17587e7e67e136f0bf2cdbf7cf6b5e20c","tid":1853103,"uid":318051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T19:16:22.000Z","msg":"人無恥就無敵<br />\n睇開啲啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T19:18:24.000Z","msg":"我朋友話佢還左錢已經老懷安為，只係唔想有人再中伏姐"},{"pid":"a7c1c7578d196373a6308fbc0f112bad226aef0d","tid":1853103,"uid":266569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T19:23:08.000Z","msg":"邊間診所做先"},{"pid":"2ebcc45eaf3aeea0e748d578a824380024e5fb14","tid":1853103,"uid":347270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7c1c7578d196373a6308fbc0f112bad226aef0d","tid":1853103,"uid":266569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T19:23:08.000Z","msg":"邊間診所做先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T19:26:17.000Z","msg":"我朋友淨係有同我講過下係尖沙咀咋"},{"pid":"92f5aba24bbc9ceff0f4a76a35089eaa7493c9cb","tid":1853103,"uid":176475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:00:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"582272a796549efa77f6c4827e389f12b201c1f1","tid":1853103,"uid":189080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:05:12.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n要比多D人睇佢個豬閪樣"},{"pid":"efa399a0a5e3c3ef81c9842cc66e9bd4f88287f8","tid":1853103,"uid":347270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"582272a796549efa77f6c4827e389f12b201c1f1","tid":1853103,"uid":189080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:05:12.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n要比多D人睇佢個豬閪樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:33:44.000Z","msg":"啱呀 佢仲成日玩人感情 以前偷人電話入過女童院 真係未見過啲女人咁唔知醜"}]}